      "rdf:value": "<L>12993<pc>74,2<k1>aBIka<k2>a-BIka<h>1<e>2\r\n<hom>1.</hom> <s>a-BIka</s> ¦ <lex>mfn.</lex> fearless, <ls>L.</ls><info lex=\"m:f:n\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
